OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy, with morning drizzle or
OL,6,Flight rain across the Peak District,
OL,7,Fany hill fog lifting with showers
OL,8,Flater. Elsewhere sunny spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping in the afternoon. Feeling
OL,10,Fwarm, but breezy in places.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy in the north of the
OL,13,Fregion with patchy rain across the
OL,14,FPeak District. Drier in the south with
OL,15,Flarger breaks in the cloud developing.
OL,16,FRelatively mild overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
