OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FGenerally cloudy start for
OL,6,Fmost, although some bright or
OL,7,Fprolonged sunny spells will develop in
OL,8,Fthe afternoon. Occasionally breezy,
OL,9,Fand becoming very warm as temperatures
OL,10,Fgradually increase.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,13,FCloudy, although some bright or
OL,14,Fprolonged sunny spells will occur.
OL,15,FOccasionally breezy, and becoming very
OL,16,Fwarm as temperatures are likely to
OL,17,Fgradually increase.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
